text: Dendrophthoe lanosa is a species of mistletoe in the family Loranthaceae; no subspecies are listed in the Catalogue of Life. Records are from Indo-China and Malesia; in Vietnam it may be called mộc ký Xiêm. == References == Danser BH (1929) In: Bull. Jard. Bot. Buitenzorg Ser.
